Season 8 in the books. Never easy to see a season end no matter when it happens, especially knowing you won’t have all the same guys in the locker room again. Blessed to cover an amazing organization on and off the field. Thanks to everyone who granted me interviews, produced/shot/edited things to make me look good, and helped put on community initiatives or events. Love what I do because of all of you!

Wasn’t the outcome we wanted but the creamsicle throwback was still amazing! Decided to try painting my first ever pair of sneakers so I bought some all-whites and added the red and orange and paint splatter plus a couple Bucco Bruce pins to the laces. The stadium, jerseys, and digital content was all 🔥 so shout out to the entire @buccaneers squad that made it all possible.
